    "rawAsk": "I need someone to own a support and sales ops migration for our startup. We run support in Notion and Airtable today, and we want HubSpot set up properly with automations, handoff docs, and operator training. Budget is around 6k to 9k. We need this done in about three weeks. AI support is fine, but I do not want a black-box setup that nobody on my team can run later."
  },
  "candidateSupplies": [
    {
      "supplyId": "sup_human_ops_migration_lead",
